# Electrical Contractors: Mitigate Labor Shortages with AI

A responsive AI-powered landing page created for electrical contractors. 
The website provides information about AI solutions and includes a playbook download form.

## Features

- Responsive design for desktop, tablet, and mobile
- AI-focused landing page
- Playbook preview section
- Lead generation form
- Form validation using JavaScript
- Smooth navigation between pages

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
- Bootstrap 5

## Project Structure
